steps.name: 1. Given I am ON dashboard page
2. When I CLICK leftMenuButton
3. And I CLICK searchPods link
4. Then I am ON searchPods page
5. And I ENTER searchInputs for search with DATA PodSearch_Success
6. Then I CLICK searchPodArrow
7. And I VERIFY correctPodsDisplayed
8. Then the correct search pod result is displayed
9. When I CLICK firstPod
10. And I VERIFY podName
11. Then the pod name is same as the first pod clicked
12. And I VERIFY forumAndEnterClsRmButtonDisplayed or not
13. Then I am ON overview page

elements.name:
1) To verify successful scenario for adding, enrolling and login with the created user with DATA InviteUser_Success
Input Data: [[Abhishek, , Yadav, adi22@gmail.com, 0, Welcome@123, Welcome@123, Default Online Site], [enrollment_success,learnerAdd_success]]

steps.name: 1. Given I am ON overview page of the pod
2. When I CLICK addParticipant button
3. Then I am ON participantResultList page
4. And I VERIFY ifLicenceAvailable to enroll user to pod
5. And I CLICK inviteLearner button
6. Then I am ON inviteUser page
7. And I PERFORM changeUserCreateStatus
8. And I ENTER valid user details with DATA InviteUser_Success
9. Then I SUBMIT the form
10. And I am ON participantResultList page
11. And I PERFORM searchParticipant
12. And I VERIFY userDisplayedOnPage
13. Then correct user is displayed on the page
14. And I VERIFY ifUserIsEnrolled to the pod
15. Then it is verified that user is enrolled to the pod
